\explain{(1)设椭圆\(C\)的标准方程为\(\frac{x^{2}}{a^{2}} + \frac{y^{2}}{b^{2}} = 1(a > b > 0)\)，
\(c = \sqrt{a^{2} - b^{2}}\)，
左右焦点为\(F_{1},F_{2}\)，\par
双曲线\(4x^{2} - \frac{4}{3}y^{2} = 1\)的焦点为\(F_{1}( - 1,0)\)和\(F_{2}(1,0)\)，
则\(c = 1\)，\par
因为\(\left| PF_{1} \right| + \left| PF_{2} \right| = \sqrt{4 + \frac{1}{2}} + \sqrt{\frac{1}{2}} = 2\sqrt{2}\)，\par
